description:
New stages will be added to the game!
They can be played in "SPECIAL".

[Details]
STAGE 4 "Haneda Airport lit up by the sunset!"
  [Difficulty level] EASY [Assigned time] 17:00～18:00

STAGE 5 "Busy at Haneda in the early afternoon!"
  [Difficulty level] HARD [Assigned time] 14:30～16:00


*The Full Version is required to access this content.
 In addition, if the latest version of the patch is required, please update the software.

*Also, it is necessary to have cleared up to "STAGE 2" of the full version to be able to access this content.
name: Commemorative Launch Pack
